  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/microsoft-nokia-asia-approval-april/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/dc9d6a39585424114827a863368bb8fe/DSC03091wtmk.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 412px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说在<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/02/doj-approval-microsoft-nokia-deal/\">美国</a>和<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/04/microsofts-nokia-acquisition-now-a-done-deal-with-final-eu-appr/\">欧洲</a>都已经顺利获得了批准，但微软和诺基亚间价值 74.5 亿美元的<a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/09/02/microsoft-will-acquire-nokias-devices-and-services-business/\">收购案</a>在亚洲审核的时间要拖得比预想中更久一些。根据双方今天发布的进度报告来看，原计划在 2014 年第一季中完成的交易如今被推迟到了 4 月，两家公司要等待亚洲相关机构给「绿灯」放行。<br />\n<br />\n不过据称必要的核查程序已经在进行当中，而微软也早已迫不及待地表示吸收诺基亚将会有利于「加速推进其行动优先、云端优先的必要发展战略」。毫无疑问，这意味着消费者将见到更多的 Windows Phone 产品上市，或者说，那些<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/24/nokia-x-elop/\">很像 Windows Phone 的手机</a>之类的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/24/microsoft-nokia-asia-approval-april/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://press.nokia.com/2014/03/24/nokia-expects-the-sale-of-substantially-all-of-its-devices-services-business-to-microsoft-to-close-in-april-2014/\" target=\"_blank\">Nokia Press</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://blogs.technet.com/b/microsoft_blog/archive/2014/03/23/an-update-on-nokia-devices-and-services-acquisition.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Microsoft Press</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/microsoft-nokia-asia-approval-april/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20855105/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/microsoft-nokia-asia-approval-april/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
